        with DeepSeek's powerful AI chat, function calling and RAG capabilities.
        Supports synchronous and asynchronous requests, automatic tool registration,
        and Spring Boot auto-configuration.

        支持同步异步请求、自动工具注册、和 Spring Boot 自动配置。
